    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e9e30800d0cd51fe1f37b0969a2c4ffc.poster.avif?t=1770631984\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e9e30800d0cd51fe1f37b0969a2c4ffc.webm?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e9e30800d0cd51fe1f37b0969a2c4ffc.mp4?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《Hats and Guns》是一款以狂野西部为背景的 Roguelike 卡牌构筑游戏。扮演不同角色，体验独特玩法。升级你的卡牌，收集强力武器和道具，在程序生成的危险沙漠腹地艰险求生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性满满的战斗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/1610aa913518cbaf9ea2366f009dbfcd.poster.avif?t=1770631984\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/1610aa913518cbaf9ea2366f009dbfcd.webm?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/1610aa913518cbaf9ea2366f009dbfcd.mp4?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗基于网格进行，以精准度为核心系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本游戏中，精准度并不决定命中目标的几率，而是决定所造成的伤害总量。没有随机性可言！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要密切关注并管理自己的站位、资源和精准度，从而将伤害最大化，在充满挑战性的对决中战斗到最后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌构筑<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e4cc3fde003a62e340e6080a7f0a6f2c.poster.avif?t=1770631984\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e4cc3fde003a62e340e6080a7f0a6f2c.webm?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/e4cc3fde003a62e340e6080a7f0a6f2c.mp4?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为 5 大类基础卡牌（精准度、速度、敏捷、反应和力量）分配超过 100 种升级方案，优化卡组并创造强力连招。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 位可玩角色<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/7500030c8436c27efa471a818d56e3a3.avif?t=1770631984\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总计 3 位独特的角色可供游玩。每位角色都有一个被动技能、一件初始武器和一套独一无二的初始卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的沙漠和诸多的道德选择<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/f137ca2e14e684409e55c3764fe42cff.poster.avif?t=1770631984\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/f137ca2e14e684409e55c3764fe42cff.webm?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261050/extras/f137ca2e14e684409e55c3764fe42cff.mp4?t=1770631984\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越荒野并谨慎地选择前进道路。收集装备，不断变强并追击你的最终目标——一位可怕的匪帮头目！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会为了复仇而变得像仇敌那般残忍无情，还是会坚守正道？</p></li></ul>",
